main_body:
The derived intervention prices for white sugar in the deficit areas of the Community shall be:
(a) EUR 64,65/100 kg for all areas in Ireland and the United Kingdom;
(b) EUR 64,65/100 kg for all areas in Portugal;
(c) EUR 64,65/100 kg for all areas in Finland;
(d) EUR 64,88/100 kg for all areas in Spain.
